Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:18.22,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,And fear not the evil shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:25.73,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,I am as a doll
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:26.02,OP_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{an3}{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,4540,4740)}仄くらき柩から
